        "content": "# PointlesSQL Audit\n\nReads PointlesSQL's Postgres metadata DB directly via Grafana's built-in PG datasource (Sprint 30.2).  \nPanels cover Phase 14 (cost-gate, external writes) + Phase 15.x (rejects, value changes) + Phase 13.11 (tool calls). No agent code, no API \u2014 just the audit tables.\n\nUse the **workspace** dropdown above to filter every panel to one or more tenants. Selecting **All** keeps the global cross-workspace view.",
