    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Open anomaly verdicts (7d)",
      "description": "Count of agent_runs in the last 7 days whose cached anomaly_severity is warn or critical (Phase 18.6). Lower is better; a sustained climb is the auditor's cue. Filtered by `$workspace` dropdown.",
